Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾經很懦弱的 Yesterday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很想大哭一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論何時也不是孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.39,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遙遠的夢想在閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將它找回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.70,0:00:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把雙眼閉上便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在心中的一個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算留下傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.88,0:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要害怕 現在是兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要放棄 Step by Step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓著夢想 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,經常也和你一起向明天邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,繼續前進 Step by Step
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想堅信著 Your Fight Jump
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.71,0:01:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想向著天空大聲呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃燒著 in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.29,0:01:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了打倒支配著遙遠星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再次成為救世主,展開了冒險旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二星界是有趣的冒險世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.64,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這裏我們要把被沙漠化了的世界恢複原本翠綠的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從奧巴鳥手上奪回星石的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再一次向基拿基拿山進發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.97,0:02:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.42,0:02:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第十一話\N炎熱的山下起雪來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.43,0:02:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好高,好高…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基拿基拿山可以說是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.83,0:02:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二星界的象徵的神聖的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你們看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.35,0:02:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在山頂上,有座叫雪石的奇怪石像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.82,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把星石放到石像的肚臍穴內的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山便會下起雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.92,0:02:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雪溶出來的水會令第二星界恢複一片翠綠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閃閃發亮的基拿基拿山嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,我一定會令雪下起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.42,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看啊!見到整座基拿基拿山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這座嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,草菇啊,草菇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的地方,怎麼爬上去啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.64,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下也有不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象先生的鼻子很長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡先生,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.81,0:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好,艾利芬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,送渡他們一程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個很好的飛行旅程呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有其他辦法的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.35,0:04:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵!快閃開…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火子,火子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你為何會在這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去哪裏是我的自由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又想打我的劍主意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.48,0:04:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道這是雪石像?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.74,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話,立即把星石放進肚臍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.73,0:05:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點,快點,鋼鐵兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡他們已去到那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種凍到頭痛的快感真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們用盡千方百計才完成的這個沙漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎能讓那渡把它恢複原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,草莓蜜瓜冰還未完成嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,草莓蜜瓜冰還未…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這個了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等我啊,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不知道什麼叫友情和幫助嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一、二、三!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真累呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起此事,你看看那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎會的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個肚臍很有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道那顆不是星石嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎會有這個可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這顆絕對是星石啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.93,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對,絕…絕對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.66,0:06:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是星石,真真正正的星石!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不行啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是救世主渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把星石帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話你便用基拿基拿山的冰河之水把那石清洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話,石頭便會變為真正的星石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你是真正的救世主的話,那便可以做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是這個第二星界的波士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,法魯戰王大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二星界的波士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.12,0:07:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦了各位,但是請你們看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刨冰,刨冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.08,0:07:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個是用基拿基拿山最後的冰河造成的刨冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,最後的冰被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也很想吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.34,0:08:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣你們便不能完成真正的星石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎會的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遺憾之餘,你們更會在此消失呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,帶走星石吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打倒那家夥的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古怪的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好,被你們看到了我正面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳,看了的話更不能饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每流進一步,便更接近地獄的入口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去的話,便會如他所說一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信著,相信著石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信石頭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信著,相信著石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信石頭…石頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.23,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家跟著我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家夥在想什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔,火子,我們也去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣去啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔和火子,首先捉緊這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,捉緊了又怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,捉緊了的話便一起飛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要自己走到生命的盡頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放棄得還真快的家夥們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在這裏!哈哈,真有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?師傅呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為何我要遇上這種事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,不要哭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,總言之大家都沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果這樣也叫沒事的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.66,0:11:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去,被活埋也只是時間的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.84,0:11:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.04,0:11:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好嘗嘗沙地獄的味道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.43,0:11:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信這石頭,絕對有出口的,絕對有的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.88,0:12:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家,幫幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了成功了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.46,0:12:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唔?這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說要相信石頭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯,我的確是這樣聽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你便跳進流沙裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為那石害我這麼慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!看,有光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厲害呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.73,0:13:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是冰的洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許這裏是地下水,凍結了的冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼這也是冰河吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.78,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯,也許溶掉這些冰,再用來清洗星石話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.03,0:13:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好滑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,法魯戰王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位,你們已逃不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是這麼多冰真令人耐不住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刨冰,刨冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,是現在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.09,0:14:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅,趁現在把星石…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵!你想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也要幫手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.20,0:15:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有點本事呢,可是這又怎樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們打算把星石…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會讓你們成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,師傅他們有危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟打我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.99,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話,便讓你看看帝皇司令官的真正力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變形了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇一跳之餘這個又怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超特大鱷魚飛戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛吧,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熔岩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,冰被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去全部會溶掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸,要保護這些冰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會讓你這樣做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到此為止了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好,不叫戰神丸來的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救…救我啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔變成廚菜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.01,0:16:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,溶吧溶吧,全部溶掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.85,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在全部溶掉之前要再吃一次,現在已確實的勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.48,0:17:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯,比起這個,冰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要保護冰啊,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.78,0:17:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍雷拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.41,0:17:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳,竟阻礙我最大的趣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混帳,超級巨炮攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,振作點,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fire!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是機會了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想吃草莓蜜瓜刨冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是空神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼是古拿瑪來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.14,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心點,渡,還有魔神在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,又是那部魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要大意,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是什麼人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部溶掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟有這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個星界已不能恢複原狀了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.10,0:19:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刨…刨冰,刨冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是剛才那大叔留下了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,火美子,不要再刨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最愛吃刨冰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.11,0:19:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀!冷得頭很痛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你幹了什麼啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這便是真正的星石嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次剛剛好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛剛好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.83,0:20:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下雪吧,下雪吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.45,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是雪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雪降下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.97,0:21:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來第二星界也恢複原狀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.41,0:22:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡,就這個樣子第三星界也拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.50,0:22:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今次是第三星界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.10,0:22:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了? 這個胸口在驅跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.47,0:22:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蹦蹦在跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.57,0:22:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop! 已不能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.56,0:22:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連你也一個勁兒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.41,0:22:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,油門不用放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.66,0:22:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直踏著 Go!Go!Go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.78,0:22:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,流星也不能代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.82,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為是速度的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,TONIGHT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.76,0:23:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密的旋律笨拙的舞蹈 Dancin'
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.81,0:23:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能夠抱到她的心 LUCKY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.91,0:23:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直望著的瞳孔湧上了 HAPPY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.13,0:23:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是 MY GIRL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.35,0:23:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今夜 MY LOVE
